<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MST Visualizer - Kruskal & Prim</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#0f172a;
color:white;
}

header{
background:linear-gradient(90deg,#2563eb,#0ea5e9);
padding:20px;
text-align:center;
font-size:28px;
font-weight:bold;
letter-spacing:1px;
}

.container{
width:90%;
margin:auto;
padding:30px 0;
}

.card{
background:#1e293b;
padding:25px;
margin-bottom:30px;
border-radius:15px;
box-shadow:0px 0px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
}

h2{
margin-bottom:15px;
color:#38bdf8;
}

pre{
background:#0f172a;
padding:20px;
border-radius:10px;
overflow:auto;
font-size:14px;
color:#22c55e;
line-height:1.5;
}

button{
padding:15px 30px;
border:none;
background:#2563eb;
color:white;
font-size:18px;
border-radius:10px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.3s;
}

button:hover{
background:#1d4ed8;
transform:scale(1.05);
}

.output{
background:#020617;
padding:20px;
border-radius:10px;
margin-top:20px;
font-size:17px;
display:none;
white-space:pre-line;
border-left:5px solid #38bdf8;
}

.graph{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
margin-top:20px;
}

svg{
background:white;
border-radius:10px;
}

.node{
fill:#2563eb;
stroke:#fff;
stroke-width:2;
}

.edge{
stroke:#444;
stroke-width:2;
}

.weight{
fill:red;
font-size:14px;
font-weight:bold;
}

.label{
fill:black;
font-size:16px;
font-weight:bold;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
Minimum Spanning Tree using Kruskal's & Prim's Algorithm
</header>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">
<h2>Graph</h2>

<div class="graph">

<svg width="650" height="350">

<!-- edges -->

<line x1="80" y1="60" x2="220" y2="50" class="edge"/>
<text x="145" y="40" class="weight">7</text>

<line x1="80" y1="60" x2="120" y2="220" class="edge"/>
<text x="75" y="150" class="weight">5</text>

<line x1="220" y1="50" x2="390" y2="60" class="edge"/>
<text x="300" y="40" class="weight">8</text>

<line x1="220" y1="50" x2="120" y2="220" class="edge"/>
<text x="170" y="130" class="weight">9</text>

<line x1="220" y1="50" x2="370" y2="180" class="edge"/>
<text x="290" y="120" class="weight">7</text>

<line x1="390" y1="60" x2="370" y2="180" class="edge"/>
<text x="390" y="120" class="weight">5</text>

<line x1="120" y1="220" x2="370" y2="180" class="edge"/>
<text x="230" y="170" class="weight">15</text>

<line x1="120" y1="220" x2="250" y2="310" class="edge"/>
